---
title: Seared Flank Steak Diane with Roasted Potatoes & Garlicky Greens
description: Steak Diane - the ultimate retro steak night meal. That creamy sauce is a taste of nostalgia, with rich, savoury notes that meld
perfectly with blushing pink steak. With a staple flavour combo like this, you have to keep the sides classic - roast potatoes and
some garlic-spiked green beans are all you could possibly need!
